    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including several dents, scratches, and areas of fading paint, while the interior has visible tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Mechanically, the car runs but needs immediate repairs to the suspension and a thorough engine tune-up to be considered reliable. This is an ideal candidate for a restoration project or for someone looking for a budget entry point willing to put in the necessary work.",
      "price": 8500.0,
